* Editor's note: This article has been updated to remove reference to McKinsey ordering Eskom to pay Trillian. You can read the updated story here. JOHANNESBURG - The North Gauteng High Court has ordered consulting firm Trillian to repay Eskom nearly R600-million. The court ruled on Tuesday that several decisions linked to Trillian were unlawful and invalid. READ: Eskom to sue Trillian to recover R600-million Eskom said last year it would sue Trillian to recover R600-million from the firm linked to the infamous Gupta family. 